data.description: Move-In Ready! A beautiful ranch with 3 main level bedrooms, spacious living & dining area.  Primary bedroom has 3/4 bath and walk-in closet.  Pella windows with blind inserts throughout.  Main floor laundry.  New roof, fascia, and gutters installed April 2023. A well established yard with UGS and fenced in backyard.  Great location near shopping, hospital and in a quiet cul-de-sac.
